Part 3 of 3. White Horse Medias Steve Wohlberg and Rob Knott discuss the film, The Letter: A Message to Our Earth, in which Pope Francis explains what humans can do to "protect our common home and save the earth. Discover whats missing, and whats false, in the message of Pope Francis.
